<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1126.94545.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Habitus, dorsal view A Brachymetra lata B Cylindrostethus hungerfordi C C. palmaris D Limnogonus hyalinus E Neogerris magnus F Tachygerris adamsoni G Rheumatobates mangrovensis H R. trinitatis I Ovatametra obesa. Scale bars: 1.0 mm (G); 2.0 mm (A-F, H, I)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/764295" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1126.94545.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Geographic distribution of Gerridae in French Guiana A Brachymetra lata, Cylindrostethus hungerfordi, C. palmaris, Limnogonus hyalinus, Neogerris magnus and Tachygerris adamsoni B Rheumatobates mangrovensis, R. trinitatis, Ovatametra obesa, Telmatometra fusca and T. parva. Circles indicate previous records; stars indicate new records." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/764296" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

